heading: 3. The area consisting of the Local Electoral Area of Shannon is
text_raw:
3. The area consisting of the Local Electoral Area of Shannon is 
prescribed as a rent pressure zone during the period commencing on 30 
November 2023 and ending on 31 December 2024. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

27 November, 2023. 

DARRAGH O’BRIEN, 

Minister for Housing, Local Government and Heritage. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 1st December, 2023.

text_raw:
EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation) 

This Order provides for the designation of the Local Electoral Area of Shannon 
as a rent pressure zone under section 24A of the Residential Tenancies Act 
2004 (as inserted by section 36 of the Planning and Development (Housing) 
and Residential Tenancies Act 2016), for the period commencing on 30 
November 2023 and ending on 31 December 2024.
